        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "1.地球水球",
        "bbox": [
          0.11343561134356113,
          0.2119118130964133,
          0.2798698279869828,
          0.23362948338269168
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(1)地球表面陆地面积占29%.海洋面积占71%.概括为“七分海洋，三分陆地” (2)分布：陆地主要集中在北半球，海洋主要集中在南半球.",
        "bbox": [
          0.1413296141329614,
          0.24086870681145114,
          0.9177126917712691,
          0.2948338269167489
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "2.十大洲和四大洋 (1)关于海洋陆地的基本概念：",
        "bbox": [
          0.11064621106462111,
          0.3376110562685094,
          0.3263598326359833,
          0.35867061533399147
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
          0.14318921431892143,
          0.36722606120434353,
          0.4686192468619247,
          0.3882856202698256
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "地域 概念 大洲 大陆和它附近的鸟屿 大陆 面积广大的陆地 岛屿 面积较小的陆地 洋 海洋的中心部分",
        "bbox": [
          0.1394700139470014,
          0.3902599539322145,
          0.7215248721524872,
          0.5429417571569596
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "是洋的一部分.位于大洋辺缘，面积较小.靠近大陆 沟通两个海洋之间的狭窄水道",
        "bbox": [
          0.26313342631334263,
          0.5521553142481079,
          0.7131566713156672,
          0.6061204343534057
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_12_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(2)海陆分布大势：",
        "bbox": [
          0.16271501627150162,
          0.6186245475485357,
          0.34309623430962344,
          0.6416584402764067
        ],
        "order": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
